          "reviewBody": "As per the guidelines set by the Council for the Indian School Certificate Examinations (CISCE), it is mandatory for schools to have a sports ground. However, I have observed that LJPS school currently lacks a dedicated sports ground for our students' sports activities.\n\nIn the absence of a proper sports ground within the school premises, The school authorities have been utilizing the nearby Government Park to fulfill this requirement. While this arrangement has temporarily addressed the issue, it is crucial to acknowledge that it does not provide an ideal environment for our students to engage in sports and physical activities.",
